data.description: Welcome to your dream country retreat on 10 sprawling acres! This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home offers the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comfort. Nestled in a serene setting, this property provides a true country feel with the convenience of modern amenities. The full basement adds an extra dimension to the home, offering ample space for storage or potential additional living areas. This property offers a rare opportunity to escape the hustle and bustle, embracing a tranquil lifestyle while enjoying the comforts of a thoughtfully updated home. Don't miss out on the chance to make this 10-acre retreat your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the serenity of country living and be close to everything!
